Ross Patterson and Dan Hollaway welcome back the author/director of "The Terrorist Whisperer" Hamody Jasim to discuss the Ukrainian flight that blew up mid-air in Iran this week, his prediction coming true on Iran's response back to the United States for the death of Qasem Soleimani, why Iran doesn't want war and why they backed down, and for the listeners subscribed to our YouTube Page-- you'll be able to see actual pictures from the Iraqis on the ground of the empty rockets Iran fired at the U.S bases.  Subscribe to Drinkin' Bros Podcast here: YouTube https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCLK5icWTfKgw6I2HIku84vg?view_as=subscriber
